nodes.text: The Oversized Package Redistribution Center was a subsidiary branch of the Interstellar Parcel Service that was located on Dune Street in Mos Eisley spaceport. Packages, shipped through the Interstellar Parcel Service, that were of a large size could be retrieved there. Such was the case when Bib Fortuna and Salacious Crumb picked up a birthday present for Jabba Desilijic Tiure.
